Diego Costa is the only Premier League player short-listed for Europe’s top individual award.

The former Atletico Madrid striker is one of 10 players short-listed for UEFA Best Player in Europe Award.

Costa won La Liga with Atletico but missed out on lifting the Champions League after losing to city rivals Real Madrid in Lisbon.

